public interface ICampStaffService

      Parameters:
      name - the name of the camp
      userGroup - the UserGroup of the camp
      location - the location of the camp
      totalSlots - the total number of slots for students
      ccmSlots - the total number of slots for committee members
      staff - the staff in-charge
      description - description of the camp
      closingDate - the LocalDateTime indicating the camp registration deadline
      dates - the list of LocalDateTime indicating the dates the camp runs on.
      visible - the visibility of camp
